315
00:28:49,094 --> 00:28:51,995
You shouldn't have looked away
when she hit me.

316
00:28:56,968 --> 00:28:59,436
And you shouldn't have walked away
from the table...

317
00:28:59,537 --> 00:29:03,064
when she twisted my words.
