318
00:29:08,546 --> 00:29:10,810
You should have hit her when she hit me!

319
00:29:10,915 --> 00:29:13,907
And you should have smacked her
when she smacked me.

320
00:29:14,018 --> 00:29:15,781
Oh, God, I love you.

321
00:29:20,425 --> 00:29:22,154
But you didn't protect me.

322
00:29:22,894 --> 00:29:24,361
And you should have.

323
00:29:24,929 --> 00:29:27,227
You pretended it wasn't happening.

324
00:29:27,432 --> 00:29:28,626
You looked away.

325
00:29:31,636 --> 00:29:33,069
And you should have.

326
00:29:34,739 --> 00:29:36,104
