433
00:38:24,135 --> 00:38:25,102
What?

434
00:38:25,970 --> 00:38:29,167
Nola's going through a very critical stage
in her therapy.

435
00:38:29,440 --> 00:38:31,374
I'm not sure she could take it.

436
00:38:32,576 --> 00:38:35,773
Are you saying that
I'm just supposed to bury the girl's mother...

437
00:38:35,880 --> 00:38:37,575
and not tell her about it?

438
00:38:37,815 --> 00:38:39,749
Yes, that's what I'm saying.

439
00:38:41,552 --> 00:38:46,080
You are one ignorant son of a bitch,
Dr. Raglan.

440
00:38:51,295 --> 00:38:53,422
Now, I have left my phone number...

441
00:38:54,332 --> 00:38:55,924
on your front desk.

442
00:38:57,068 --> 00:39:00,299
If I don't hear from my daughter
by tomorrow afternoon...

443
00:39:01,972 --> 00:39:04,099
I'm coming back up here to get her.

444
00:39:10,114 --> 00:39:11,809
Shall I have him stopped?

445
00:39:12,516 --> 00:39:13,949
No, it's all right.

446
00:39:14,685 --> 00:39:15,777
He's drunk.

447
00:39:58,262 --> 00:40:00,230
Hi. Sorry I'm late.

448
00:40:01,699 --> 00:40:04,361
- You two look like you're having fun.
