449
00:40:05,369 --> 00:40:08,065
Daddy, Ms. Mayer said she was starving.

450
00:40:08,272 --> 00:40:10,604
Can we feed her at our place tonight?

451
00:40:10,708 --> 00:40:11,675
Candy...

452
00:40:12,510 --> 00:40:14,171
We could if she wanted to.

453
00:40:16,380 --> 00:40:17,745
What do you think?

454
00:40:18,349 --> 00:40:19,475
Well, I...

455
00:40:20,084 --> 00:40:22,348
We could talk after Candy goes to bed.

456
00:40:24,955 --> 00:40:25,922
Sure.

457
00:40:32,563 --> 00:40:35,123
As soon as Candy realized
she had me alone...

458
00:40:35,232 --> 00:40:37,928
she got me to play
"mother and daughter" with her.

459
00:40:40,204 --> 00:40:43,002
