462
00:40:53,317 --> 00:40:54,807
It's not just you.

463
00:40:56,954 --> 00:41:00,219
Sometimes when I'm being easy on myself,
I say, "It's not your fault.

464
00:41:00,324 --> 00:41:01,791
"You got taken in.

465
00:41:02,359 --> 00:41:05,385
"You got involved with a woman
who married you for your sanity...

466
00:41:05,496 --> 00:41:07,191
"hoping it would rub off."

467
00:41:09,300 --> 00:41:11,768
Instead, it started to work the other way.

468
00:41:21,145 --> 00:41:22,112
Hello?

469
00:41:22,413 --> 00:41:24,108
It's Barton Kelly, Frank.

470
00:41:24,482 --> 00:41:25,676
How are you?

471
00:41:26,116 --> 00:41:27,174
Just mediocre.

472
00:41:27,885 --> 00:41:29,011
How are you?

473
00:41:30,621 --> 00:41:32,282
I made a mistake.

474
00:41:33,090 --> 00:41:34,955
I came back to the old place.

475
00:41:36,093 --> 00:41:37,458
It's got me.

476
00:41:39,530 --> 00:41:41,293
I'm depressed as hell.

477
00:41:42,333 --> 00:41:44,665
Barton, get in a cab, will you?

478
00:41:45,269 --> 00:41:47,601
- Just tell him to take...
- That's not all.

479
00:41:48,439 --> 00:41:49,804
There's Nola, too.

480
00:41:52,576 --> 00:41:53,508
How do you mean?

481
00:41:54,044 --> 00:41:56,171
I went up to that place to see her.

482
00:41:57,414 --> 00:41:59,348
They wouldn't even let me talk to her.

483
00:42:00,484 --> 00:42:02,952
They said no to me, her own father!

484
00:42:03,053 --> 00:42:04,020
Jesus.

485
00:42:04,455 --> 00:42:07,049
So I'm going back up there, to Somafree.

486
00:42:07,791 --> 00:42:10,351
We'll leave just as soon as you get here.

487
00:42:10,461 --> 00:42:11,519
Soon as I get there?

488
00:42:11,629 --> 00:42:13,290
I'll be waiting for you.

489
00:42:13,397 --> 00:42:15,661
I know you'll want to go up there with me.

490
00:42:16,433 --> 00:42:19,493
- You're not far from here, are you?
- Barton, listen to me.

491
00:42:19,603 --> 00:42:22,231
I don't think that's a very smart thing to do.

492
00:42:22,339 --> 00:42:25,137
I'm doing it, with or without you.

493
00:42:27,044 --> 00:42:28,170
Okay.

494
00:42:28,746 --> 00:42:31,374
I'm only about 15 minutes away. Wait for me.

495
00:42:31,482 --> 00:42:32,710
I'll be there.

496
00:42:33,317 --> 00:42:34,978
You're a good lad.

497
00:42:37,187 --> 00:42:39,951
We'll go up there together,
and kick their ass.

498
00:42:41,559 --> 00:42:43,322
I'm waiting on you.

499
00:42:49,600 --> 00:42:52,467
I've a feeling
I've just been recruited to baby-sit.

500
00:42:53,504 --> 00:42:56,098
Would you? It'd take 45 minutes.

501
00:42:56,874 --> 00:42:58,068
He's drunk.

502
00:42:58,175 --> 00:43:01,702
He'll drive his car off a bridge,
unless I talk some sense into him.

503
00:43:01,812 --> 00:43:03,074
45 minutes?

504
00:43:03,180 --> 00:43:04,738
That's all it'll take.

505
00:43:05,215 --> 00:43:06,182
Okay.

506
00:43:06,550 --> 00:43:07,517
Thanks.

507
00:43:08,552 --> 00:43:10,452
Help yourself to some coffee.

508
00:43:11,689 --> 00:43:12,656
Here.

509
00:43:14,425 --> 00:43:16,222
Look at this while I'm gone.

510
00:43:16,493 --> 00:43:18,654
